title: MorticianCall.Call
body:
<<set $morgueUnlocked to true>>
<<thinkingFont Dialogue>>
Huh? My phone...
<<endThinkingFont Dialogue>>
->Answer
Hi Detective, it's Jonas down at the morgue.
I've got the victim on the slab here if you want to get my reports.
->Okay I'll head down right away
    <<loadLevel MapObject Morgue>>
->I've got some things to clear up. I'll head down later.
